Pierre Marie Jean Robiquet , notice biographique sur cths.fr
Jean Robiquet (6 July 1874 – 26 March 1960) was a French art historian, art critic and curator.
Jean Robiquet (6 July 1874 – 26 March 1960) was a French art historian, art critic and curator.
Attached to the Musée Carnavalet in 1897, he became assistant curator in 1904, then chief curator from 1919 to his retirement in 1934.
